  ('public-health-specialist-moex-01358', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-111-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '若針對某一社區居民隨機抽樣300人，此樣本之平均年齡為55歲，已知其平均年齡顯著不同 於 64 歲，假設社區居民的年齡呈常態分布，則下列何者比較可能是平均年齡的雙尾 95%信 賴區間？', '["（57,71）", "（48,62）", "（54,74）", "（45,65）"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3b26ea176416", "answer_pdf_sha1": "af1063b3ceba", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "110", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生物統計學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-01359', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-111-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '根據COVID-19全球疫情地圖，得知臺灣疫苗接種覆蓋率86.79%，如果隨機在臺灣抽取一萬 人，計算此樣本的疫苗接種覆蓋率，此樣本觀察到接種疫苗人數的變異數為下列何者？', '["1146", "1321", "7532", "8679"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3b26ea176416", "answer_pdf_sha1": "af1063b3ceba", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "110", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生物統計學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-01360', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-111-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '針對統計檢定力（statisticalpower,1-β）的敘述，下列何者較正確？', '["當虛無假設為真的，卻推翻虛無假設的機率", "當虛無假設是真的，卻沒有推翻虛無假設的機率", "當對立假設是真的，卻推翻虛無假設的機率", "當對立假設是真的，卻沒有推翻虛無假設的機率"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3b26ea176416", "answer_pdf_sha1": "af1063b3ceba", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "110", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生物統計學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 21, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-01361', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-111-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '某個研究罹患癌症的危險因子分析結果如下表所示，以0.05的型一誤差（typeIerrorrate）來 判定，下列敘述何者錯誤？ 勝算比 95%信賴區間 oddsratio Gender male 0.94 (0.64,1.37) female 1.00 Age（years） age<40 1.00 40<=age<60 1.52 (0.96,2.41) 60<=age 2.21 (1.28,3.80)', '["男性罹患癌症的危險性較女性高", "40至60歲的人相較於40歲以下罹患癌症的危險性未達統計上顯著性", "年紀60歲以上者相較於40歲以下罹患癌症的危險性較高", "這個表格的結果是使用羅吉斯迴歸（logisticregression）計算而得"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3b26ea176416", "answer_pdf_sha1": "af1063b3ceba", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "110", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生物統計學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 22, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-01362', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-111-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '一項探討醫學檢驗值與胰臟癌關係的病例對照研究，研究過程中收集了飯前血糖、飯後血糖、 糖化血色素及總膽固醇，若想要了解有或沒有胰臟癌之相關醫學檢驗值互相校正後，何項相 關醫學檢驗值較有顯著意義，下列何種統計方法最合適？', '["簡單線性迴歸", "複線性迴歸", "簡單羅吉斯迴歸", "複羅吉斯迴歸"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3b26ea176416", "answer_pdf_sha1": "af1063b3ceba", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "110", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生物統計學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 23, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-01363', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-111-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '一組100人的隨機樣本，進行暴露（X）與疾病（Y）的關係研究，變數設定以及研究結果整 理為下列2×2的列聯表，如果以羅吉斯迴歸分析之後，截距β 的估計值為何？ 0 有病（Y=1） 沒病（Y=0） 有暴露（X=1） 10 20 無暴露（X=0） 40 30', '["10/40", "20/30", "log(10/20)", "log(40/30)"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3b26ea176416", "answer_pdf_sha1": "af1063b3ceba", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "110", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生物統計學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 24, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-01364', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-111-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '利用羅吉斯迴歸分析有無用藥（Treatment,yesvs.no）對於疾病的治癒效果（Cure,yesvs.no）， 發現在男性族群中，有用藥物治療的病患勝算（odds），是安慰劑病患勝算的2倍，但是女性 族群中，勝算比降為1.2倍。請問這個研究中，對於性別變數的敘述何者最適切？', '["性別變數是干擾因子（confounder）", "性別變數修飾了藥物與治癒的關係（effectmodifier）", "性別變數只是共變數（covariate）", "性別變數可以預測疾病"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3b26ea176416", "answer_pdf_sha1": "af1063b3ceba", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "110", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生物統計學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 25, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-01365', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-111-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '想研究高中生男女的體脂肪有無差異，隨機收集了年齡相近的13位男生與11位女生，描述 統計如下所示。欲以twosamplet-test檢定，若假設兩組變異數相等，此變異數（pooledvariance） 的估計值最接近之數值為何？ 組別 樣本數（n） 平均數（x） 標準差（s） 女同學 11 22 5 男同學 13 15 7', '["35", "36", "37", "38"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3b26ea176416", "answer_pdf_sha1": "af1063b3ceba", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "110", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生物統計學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 26, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-01366', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-111-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '分析40位12～17歲青少年的年齡（Age）與身高（公分）的關聯性分析，得到下表，下列敘 述何者正確？ Variable Estimate Lowerboundof95%CI Upperboundof95%CI Intercept 96.82 70.09 123.56 Age 4.44 2.54 6.34 R2=0.37', '["皮爾森相關係數（Pearsoncorrelationcoefficient）是0.37，迴歸係數（regressioncoefficient） 是4.44", "皮爾森相關係數是0.61，迴歸係數是4.44", "皮爾森相關係數是0.61，迴歸係數是96.82", "身高有37%可以被年齡所解釋，迴歸係數是96.82"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3b26ea176416", "answer_pdf_sha1": "af1063b3ceba", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "110", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生物統計學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 27, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL)
